name: Fyatracker.GitHub.io
body:
This organization is currently in the development phase.  There is a message board, and we can chat on FireTalk (Mesh Networking IM Client - compatible with iPhone, Android, and Windows phone.  I'm not sure if there is a web version, but issues like that will be addressed as I develop the site.  Please contact me with questions/concerns/methods of encryption and communication safety.  Never be afraid of asking for help.  I would prefer to give telephone support @ 0300 in the morning if it means plugging any possible security leaks.   

* Firechat (listed in Play Store/App Store
* ShadowTalk (listed in Stores)
* ProtonMail
* **http://users.smartgb.com/g/g.php?a=s&i=g18-82484-56**
